%% Sequence: Launch Assistant (Fase 3)
%% Usuario lanza Assistant con contexto del eslabón
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Usuario (Backoffice)
    participant API as Backoffice API
    participant Context as Context Bundle Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Assistant as Assistant (Electron)

    User->>API: POST /api/v1/echelons/:id/launch<br/>Auth + Tenant
    API->>Context: getContextBundle(echelonId, orgId)
    Context->>DB: echelon, requiredFields, summaries, decisionLinks, sessions
    Context-->>API: ContextBundleResponse
    API->>API: deepLinkUrl = APP_URL/echelon/:id?contextVersion=v
    API-->>User: 200 { echelonId, deepLinkUrl, context }

    Note over User,Assistant: Usuario abre deep link en Assistant
    User->>Assistant: Abre deepLinkUrl (app://... o https://...)
    Assistant->>Assistant: Bootstrap con context (requiredFields, summaries, decisionAnchors)
    Assistant->>API: GET /api/v1/context/:echelonId (refresh context si necesario)
    API->>API: getContextBundleFromCache(echelonId)
    alt cache hit
        API-->>Assistant: 200 cached bundle
    else cache miss
        API->>Context: getContextBundle(...)
        API->>API: setContextBundleCache(echelonId, bundle)
        API-->>Assistant: 200 bundle
    end
